Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:18.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}夢を見る少し手前で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:22.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}置いてきたものはなんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:27.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}忘れてしまいたくはないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:30.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}時折ふっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:33.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}記憶の隅に浮かぶのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:37.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}ふんわりぼやけたセピア色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:45.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}目の前を塞ぐ日々の向こう　少しずつ遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:53.42,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}大体なんで息を切らして走ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:59.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}スピード上げてゆくほど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:03.55,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}立ち止まることが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:10.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}早くなる鼓動に触れココに居ると確かめた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:18.42,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}ココロの奥の小さな声に耳を澄ましたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:28.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}{\be5}包み込む世界が晴れ広がるよ明日へ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------EDCN-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:18.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}就要坠入梦乡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:22.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}把什么放在了手边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:27.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}明明不想忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:30.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}却又无法想起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:33.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}时而浮现在记忆角落里的往日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:37.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}轻轻染上岁月的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:45.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}一纵即逝　渐行渐离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:53.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}气喘吁吁地奔跑又是为何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:59.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}愈是加快步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:03.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}就愈是畏惧停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:10.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}抚摸加速的心跳确认了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:18.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}侧耳倾听　那微弱的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:28.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}{\be5}却发现　天高海阔　直至未来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------TEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到车站附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  要来了啊  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷…冷静…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的客人交给菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你来负责
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给菜子那么重的担子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有客人指名要你接待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:01:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  不如让有血缘关系的绪花去接待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在考虑范围之外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就老板娘您亲自出马…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在考虑范围之外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是见到那位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计会忍不住打她几嘴巴子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  绪花为什么特意要引狼入室呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花带来的可是贵客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有过什么矛盾  客人就是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄做好本分的事就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己能不能保持客观就不得而知了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长途开车辛苦了彻君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  越来越破了  感觉怪可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人也一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  变得越来越…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以下省略哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}快接待客人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒肚都出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我带您去房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个调动气氛专家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  绪花呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣的款式一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有不少地方已经能让客人自己选浴衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让客人有所期待也是有必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请  请用茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包装上精心设计下会更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如在水果上再花些功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近盛产柚子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们服务员来说也可以多个可以和客人聊天的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职业病又犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自言自语很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生得一对水汪汪的大眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你就不能冷静一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不知道我姐的恶行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假作业全推给年纪小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压岁钱也被她敲诈殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得你会喜欢崇子小姐那种蛮横的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提了许多改进旅馆的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建议？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如浴衣还有茶点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了又能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  并不是因为是姐姐的意见才…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是本着尊重客人意见的前提下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花真勤快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚回来  那么快就投入工作了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了  才一眨眼的功夫  就变回平时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在东京举着标语牌的我也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿孝在家庭餐馆里的我也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不是平时的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这番景像才是我所熟悉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello  女服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去个地方  陪我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要我陪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着高跟鞋爬坡很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝客人的请求  要是出了问题你要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这鬼地方还真是什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这附近有个雪洞祭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我唯一喜欢的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么能够实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许个希望能和阿孝和好如初的愿望试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被  被甩了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人多得满街跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你矮矮胖胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好歹是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也多少有点姿色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要只在这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要只在这种时候才摆出一副母亲架子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你把这旅馆吹上了天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才特意来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是你被男人甩而消沉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个旅馆好在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来伤得不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被男人甩而消沉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被男人甩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是被甩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻  前菜就交给了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这季节应该是白鱚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是天妇罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我们是十年如一日大概又要招人笑话了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的预想其实和期待是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意辜负别人的期待可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要在其他地方让我大吃一惊才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如多准备一些式样之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全盘否定还比这个来得轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也被摆了一道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到入浴的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么不懂变通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫除的时间应该迎合客人的动向随机应变才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何时都能泡个够才是温泉的可贵之处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那后颈上美艳的肌肤…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是个让人头疼的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  果然是个很出色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关料理的基本知识也没有说错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和少爷带来的崇子小姐可是天差地别
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐说要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要崇子小姐在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算能和姐姐势均力敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候你还想着去依靠外人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不单是喜翠庄  更是我们家  四十万家的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是亲女儿  她也是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次我回避了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个人情感太重的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不能很好地完成工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三笠先生的亲人  她的女儿要是来了该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…一定要准备两条浴巾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那夫人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她喜欢热茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水壶的水温要调高一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于初来的客人  要调查他的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他下次光临的时候  投其所好进行接待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  那位客人虽然是初来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又不能说是初来客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位客人的情况  你和我都非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位客人和老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管是不同的类型  但却有共通之处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的话能让人信服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你们太高看那位客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我是老板娘插手厨房事务也太过不合常理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管这是我再清楚不过的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能莲先生让我用一下厨房吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给藤之间的客人准备被褥的活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让我来办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是平常的绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好下功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  这是专为您准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这煮竹轮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为旅馆的料理还真是老土
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意做了我最喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  豆丁老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要洗澡了  能出去一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人马上就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你在不在  都要继续清扫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被看的话就去厨房洗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张床单还没有干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不抱着卷成桶状的床单就睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就夹着绪花睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请去拜托你男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿会说这种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我眼里  妈妈与其说是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如说是个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得真帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Call最好增加到三次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子早上很难被叫醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡相难看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边就算是夏天  晚上还是很凉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐还是准备粥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜果汁也比较适合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是第一次能单独和老板娘聊那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且谈妈妈的事也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘是我的外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所当然也是老妈的母亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤之间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以来点酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加热到温
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来三瓶啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有清凉饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有艺伎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艺伎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个时候恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就老太太和小女孩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有别的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么见外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子喝果汁居然都能醉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她太容易相信别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  知道什么呢  绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很珍惜阿孝的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去告白不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,察觉到自己喜欢阿孝的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十万家的女人怎么能被甩了一两次就轻言放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说老妈你也是拼命追才把老爸追到手的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人可固执了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前四次都以失败告终
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事不过五啊  真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不想再折腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝已经有他自己的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要回东京吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到阿孝他平时的生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再去习惯不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的不是的不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已经有自己的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在喜翠庄的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果比起恋爱选择了工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是四十万家的女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你总是吊儿郎当的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也有在雪愿！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也是  外婆也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在雪愿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是得到了女儿的认同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那父母也就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没有听到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝得真爽快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去像在加班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指皋月小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈也是  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是我被排除在外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能喝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么就结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈是这么不能喝的么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了一个梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是负责这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈还真是轻呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让她放心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可什么都没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要继续做一个讨厌的老妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是说好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的干不下去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这种时候摆出母亲的架子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  让我最后潇洒一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爷也保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我说都写了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年如一日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说着轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不与时俱进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围会变得停滞不前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从默默无闻变到尽人皆知的十年如一日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非常困难的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄永远在进步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保持不变的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了延续十年如一日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到了大家的志气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个温暖又舒适的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夸奖我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是盛赞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈来这里后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想过阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一次也没想过要回东京
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是恢复不了和阿孝的关系才不回东京
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方有我的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择这份生活的不是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢在喜翠庄工作的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢外婆…喜欢老板娘和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也喜欢阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝  一直以来真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.00,0:23:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.98,0:23:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}都把比赛用泳衣带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}不是要向她告白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花想做女服务员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太了解结名同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
